│ the transformed code makes this path unreachable.\n\n2. Analyzing `opt`'s Log: The log shows that the pass removes all switch cases and creates a 'default.unreachable' block with an unreachable instruction. │
│ The key issue is in the logic that determines if the default destination is unreachable based on the constant range analysis.\n\n3. Root Cause Analysis: The bug is in line 418 of                             │
