│  52 /// GlobalValues), it never makes sense to RAUW them.                                                                                                                                                      │
│  53 ///                                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│  54 /// These do not have use lists. It is illegal to inspect the uses. These behave                                                                                                                           │
│  55 /// as if they have no uses (i.e. use_empty() is always true).                                                                                                                                             │
